title: Coke Weed "Blue Flag" : Converse Red Light Sessions
description:
The psych rock quintet from Maine bought their hypnotic sound to the Red Light Studio at Converse Rubber Tracks in Brooklyn during CMJ festival last September. 

Red Light Sessions are special live performances filmed in partnership with Amsterdam-based digital radio station Red Light Radio.
